<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><TimeML><TIMEX3 tid="t0" functionInDocument="CREATION_TIME"/>Seve Ballesteros will be <EVENT eid="e1" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="FUTURE" aspect="PROGRESSIVE" polarity="POS" modality="none">playing</EVENT> in  <TIMEX3 tid="t1" type="DATE">next month</TIMEX3>'s US Open after all. The USGA <EVENT eid="e2" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="PAST" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">decided</EVENT> <TIMEX3 tid="t2" type="DATE">Tuesday</TIMEX3> to <EVENT eid="e3" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="INFINITIVE" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">give</EVENT> the Spanish  star a special exemption.&#13;
