<TIMEX3 tid="t3" type="DATE">Earlier this week</TIMEX3> Ballesteros, winner of three Opens and two Masters, had  <EVENT eid="e5" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="PAST" aspect="PERFECTIVE" polarity="POS" modality="none">vowed</EVENT> to <EVENT eid="e6" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="INFINITIVE" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">skip</EVENT> the US open if he was not <EVENT eid="e7" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="PAST" aspect="NONE" polarity="NEG" modality="none">given</EVENT> an automatic place.&#13;
