"It's not a matter of pride. I just feel I <EVENT eid="e18" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="PRESENT" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">deserve</EVENT> an invitation. I have  been <TIMEX3 tid="t5" type="DURATION">20 years</TIMEX3> on tour and I have proved myself. I don't <EVENT eid="e19" class="I_STATE" tense="PRESENT" aspect="NONE" polarity="NEG" modality="none">think</EVENT> I have to <EVENT eid="e20" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="PRESENT" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">prove</EVENT>  anything," <EVENT eid="e21" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="PAST" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">fumed</EVENT> the Spaniard.&#13;
