"Both Seve Ballesteros and Ben Crenshaw have <EVENT eid="e23" class="OCCURRENCE" tense="PRESENT" aspect="PERFECTIVE" polarity="POS" modality="none">played</EVENT> well recently," <EVENT eid="e24" class="REPORTING" tense="PAST" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">said</EVENT>  USGA executive committee vice president Judy Bell, <EVENT eid="e25" class="REPORTING" tense="PRESPART" aspect="NONE" polarity="POS" modality="none">announcing</EVENT> the exemptions.&#13;
